                                                               Public free use licence v1(PFUL)
================================================================================================================================================================================

1	Contributor is a individual who makes changes to media or software. A contributor can also be a firm , publishing agency or other wise.
2	The way this is used is also important the software or media can not be disguise else. It must be used for good and not for bad e.g. coding software for a nuclear missile would not be allowed. While making a learning source is allowed and embraced .
3	The producers can make direct changes to there repository but not else were that includes the code from this source.
4	The license can not change when redistributed 
5	The code or media must stay in the public domain if the licences changes
